SUMMARY:A Town Hall on Security and Surveillance
DTSTAMP:20260325T063301Z
DTSTART:20260327T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Mayor Wilson and Executive Director of the South Seattle E
	merald\\\, Florangela Davila for a conversation on security\\\, surveillan
	ce\\\, and their impacts on Seattle’s communities. This event brings Mayor
	 Wilson on stage and in dialogue for a shared look at the challenges and o
	pportunities shaping the city right now. The evening will begin with a mod
	erated conversation\\\, followed by time for audience Q&A. Together\\\, we
	’ll explore questions of safety\\\, privacy\\\, and public trust — and con
	sider how policy decisions resonate across the city’s creative and civic l
	andscape. Above all\\\, this is a chance to gather: to listen\\\, exchange
	 ideas\\\, and reflect together on how Seattle can move forward in this mo
	ment.\n\nhttps://townhallseattle.org/event/seattle-surveillance/\n\nFrom T
	own Hall Seattle
URL:https://townhallseattle.org/event/seattle-surveillance/
